{"tid":1431934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"七月鬼多 同道提防","createTime":"2019-08-08T06:03:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T11:58:52.000Z","uid":107060,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"65ddd3b35913987e3ee6c8de911e572e12bb89b2","tid":1431934,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:03:04.000Z","msg":"Source:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/makehkgreatagain/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fmakehkgreatagain%2F&d=zOUAwLUjYZjm4ccI%2FGD8rNTLU9NF7cMiG%2FeCYohcYb8%3D&h=6d5e410f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/makehkgreatagain/</a><br />\n是否最近都有一種感覺︰每逢大戰過後，總是特別多遊魂野鬼扮同路人，叫你停一停、諗一諗？更作出多角度分析，解釋和理非為何應該憎你恨你，好像準備跟你割蓆一樣？<br />\n<br />\n林鄭叫你諗一諗香港安定繁榮、楊光叫你諗一諗14億中國人、連登鬼叫你諗一諗自己是否迷失同享受權力......享受權力？WTF？享受上前線吃催淚彈的權力嗎？這種新穎的想法我還是第一次聽到，從連登鬼口中聽到。真正上過前線的人，不會叫你諗，因為大家都知道五大訴求、民主自治，成功之前諗乜都係多餘，最多回家沖涼嗰陣會諗︰今日丟咗副Gear好撚肉赤！<br />\n<br />\n遲疑的同道，你們只是還沒有習慣左膠內奸扮自己人，然後分化割蓆而已。我們五年前看過，不想你們經歷同一種痛苦，所以才有這個專頁出現。<br />\n<br />\n該想的，是那些已經犧牲的烈士、我們流過的血汗、那官員黑警的嘴臉，你有停下來的理由嗎？想到13歲的同道被捕、少女被公然施暴、平民無辜被斬、中TG，叫你停下來的，肯撚定就是鬼！沒辦法，最接近晨曦的時刻，總是最黑暗、最多鬼的。<br />\n<br />\n盂蘭盛會心中不必驚慌，慎終追遠是我們的傳統美德，勤力點燒燒街衣吧，勝利在望。"},{"pid":"341c5d4a3df83953f28c140913cac85ca3011c72","tid":1431934,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:37:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ac6402e3b7c6d279ece5a86927c5586ae02f0a","tid":1431934,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T06:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91920f4260ad95be6c47f74c4d4b7f6d775fba7","tid":1431934,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ada59cc836e5ebde45aceff254abfc5fbaf51402","tid":1431934,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T15:25:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a991f8c323e49e09f1b433ab15104d0e9417dcb","tid":1431934,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:58:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75e8a916418d5c8ad7979e2fb3f7c79b466f35b1","tid":1431934,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbdc20d6c8b04b1b84b5c500631e1f8ae546218d","tid":1431934,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T07:58:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc78cff9cce21d63d01bc50e52b6b761e8779e66","tid":1431934,"uid":107060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T11:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}